                                </div>
                                <div class="card-footer small text-muted">Updated yesterday at 11:59 PM</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="card mb-3">
                                <div class="card-header">
                                    <i class="fa fa-area-chart"></i> Issued licenses / month
